Open D Express Open D Express is a web-based chatbot that I developed for OpenDialog. Open D Express offers delivery services (e.g., scheduling the delivery of an online order). The chatbot was developed as a demo to showcase OpenDialog's software capabilities, and it is now part of OpenDialog Academy and OpenDialog's documentation.
